No stress—let’s skip downloads entirely and build the site right in GitHub so Netlify updates instantly.

What you’ll do (on your phone)

1. Open your repo (the one linked to Netlify).


2. Tap Add file → Create new file.



File 1 — index.html

Paste this and Commit:

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>Uchechi Beauty WIG'S STORE</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Luxury wigs, shoes, bags. Secure orders via WhatsApp." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
<header>
  <div class="container nav">
    <div class="logo">Uchechi Beauty <span>WIG'S</span> STORE</div>
    <div class="actions socials">
      <a href="https://instagram.com/uchechi_beauty_wigstore" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
      <a href="https://www.facebook.com/uchechi.beauty01" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<main class="container">
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Shop Luxury Wigs, Shoes & Bags</h1>
    <p class="lead">Fast response on WhatsApp • Worldwide shipping • Secure site</p>
    <div id="grid" class="grid"></div>
  </section>

  <footer class="footer">© <span id="year"></span> Uchechi Beauty WIG'S STORE. All rights reserved.</footer>
</main>

<a class="whatsapp-float" href="https://wa.me/2349060135725?text=Hello%20Uchechi!%20I%27d%20like%20to%20order." target="_blank">WA</a>

<script>document.getElementById('year').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();</script>
<script src="/assets/app.js" defer></script>
</body>
</html>

3. Again tap Add file → Create new file.



File 2 — assets/styles.css

Paste and Commit:

:root{--bg:#0b0b0d;--card:#141418;--gold:#f6c453;--text:#f8fafc;--muted:#cbd5e1;}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{margin:0;padding:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Ubuntu,Cantarell,"Helvetica Neue",Arial}
.container{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:16px}
header{position:sticky;top:0;background:#0b0b0df2;border-bottom:1px solid #1f2937}
.nav{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:12px 0}
.logo{font-weight:900;letter-spacing:.5px}
.logo span{color:var(--gold)}
.actions a{color:var(--text);margin-left:14px;opacity:.95}
.hero{padding:22px 0}
h1{font-size:34px;margin:10px 0}
p.lead{color:var(--muted);margin-top:0}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:12px}
@media(min-width:700px){.grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);}}
.card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid #27272a;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden}
.card img{width:100%;height:220px;object-fit:cover;background:#111}
.card .pad{padding:12px}
.badge{display:inline-block;background:#1f2937;color:var(--gold);border:1px solid #374151;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:9999px;font-size:12px;margin-bottom:6px}
.price{font-weight:800;color:var(--gold);margin-top:8px}
.cta{display:inline-block;margin-top:8px;background:var(--gold);color:#000;padding:10px 14px;border-radius:10px;font-weight:800;text-decoration:none}
.footer{color:#94a3b8;margin:28px 0 60px}
.whatsapp-float{position:fixed;right:16px;bottom:16px;width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;background:#25D366;color:#000;font-weight:900;text-decoration:none}
.socials a{margin-right:12px}

4. Again Add file → Create new file.



File 3 — assets/app.js

Paste and Commit:

const products=[
  {title:'30" Body Wave 360 Lace Wig',price:'₦180,000',img:'https://placehold.co/600x400/0b0b0d/EEE?text=30in+Lace+Wig',cat:'Wigs'},
  {title:"Men’s Luxury Shoes",price:'₦45,000',img:'https://placehold.co/600x400/0b0b0d/EEE?text=Luxury+Shoes',cat:'Shoes'},
  {title:'Luxury Handbag – Gold',price:'₦71,000',img:'https://placehold.co/600x400/0b0b0d/EEE?text=Gold+Bag',cat:'Bags'}
];
function render(){
  const grid=document.getElementById('grid'); grid.innerHTML='';
  products.forEach(p=>{
    const el=document.createElement('div'); el.className='card';
    el.innerHTML=`<img src="${p.img}" alt="${p.title}">
      <div class="pad">
        <div class="badge">${p.cat}</div>
        <div style="font-weight:800">${p.title}</div>
        <div class="price">${p.price}</div>
        <a class="cta" target="_blank"
           href="https://wa.me/2349060135725?text=${encodeURIComponent('Hello! I want to order: '+p.title)}">
           Order on WhatsApp</a>
      </div>`;
    grid.appendChild(el);
  });
}
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded',render);

Finish up

After the third commit, Netlify will auto-deploy.

Open your link: https://uchechibeautystore.netlify.app ✅


If you prefer the ZIP again later, I can re-generate—but this GitHub method won’t expire and works right away.

